<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Teen ager provides dog walking in Flagstaff Arizona">
    <meta name="keywords" content="dog walking">
    <meta name="author" content="Sheena Jessee">
    <title>Puppy Palz Dog Walking</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/style.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/bower_components/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="bower_components/bootstrap-calendar/css/calendar.css">
   
   
	<script type="text/javascript" src="bower_components/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="bower_components/underscore/underscore-min.js"></script>	
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="scripts/script.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="bower_components/bootstrap-calendar/js/calendar.js"></script>
    
</head>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div id="title">
            <h1> Puppy Palz</h1>
            <h3> Dog walking and Pet sitting </h3>
        </div>

        <div id="dropDownMenu">
            <ul id="menuList">
                <!--<li id="menu">Menu</li>-->
                <li class="listItems" id="signout">Sign Out</li>
                <li class="listItems" id="about">About Me </li>
                <li class="listItems" id="faq">FAQ/Rates </li>
                <li class="listItems" id="setUp"> Set Up Walking Appointment</li>
               

            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div id="mainImgDiv">
            <img src="image/dog.jpg" id="mainImg" alt="person walking a dog" />
        </div>
		<div id="setAppointment">
		   <div id="appointmentContainer">    

		      <div id="calendarContainer">
			      <h2>Chloe's Dog Walking Appointment Schedular</h2>
			      <button class ="setButtons" id="schedule" type="button">Schedule Appointment</button>
				  <button class ="setButtons" id="cancel" type="button">Cancel Appointment</button>
			      <button class ="setButtons" id="month" type="button">Monthly View</button>
			      <button class ="setButtons" id="week" type="button">Weekly View</button>
			      <button class ="setButtons" id="day" type="button">Daily View</button>
				  <div id="appointmentForm">
			        <form id="appForm" action="/insertEvent" method="post">
			           <h3>Select Date For Walk</h3>					  
			           <input type="date" id="date" name="date">
					   <h3>Select the time of the walk</h3>
			           <input type="radio" id="time1" name="time" value="16:00">
			           <label for="time1">4:00 - 4:25</label>
			           <input type="radio" id="time2" name="time" value="16:30">
			           <label for="time2">4:30 - 4:55</label>
			           <input type="radio" id="time3" name="time" value="17:00">
			           <label for="time3">5:00 - 5:25</label><br>
					   <button type="submit">Schedule Walk</button>
			        </form>
                  </div>
				  <div id="cancelAppointment">
			        <form id="cancelForm" action="/deleteEvent" method="post">
			           <h3>Select Date Of Walk To Cancel</h3>					  
			           <input type="date" id="canceldate" name="date">
					   <h3>Select the time of the walk</h3>
			           <input type="radio" id="canceltime1" name="time" value="16:00">
			           <label for="canceltime1">4:00 - 4:25</label>
			           <input type="radio" id="canceltime2" name="time" value="16:30">
			           <label for="canceltime2">4:30 - 4:55</label>
			           <input type="radio" id="canceltime3" name="time" value="17:00">
			           <label for="canceltime3">5:00 - 5:25</label><br>
					   <button type="submit">Cancel Walk</button>
			        </form>
				 </div>
				 <div id="validateEvent">
				 </div>
			  
		         <div id="calendar"></div>
		      </div>			 
			 
			  <div class="petContainer">
		         <div class="petCollage">
                    <img src="image/dog3.jpg" id="dogImg3" alt="a dog" />
                    <img src="image/cat1.jpg" id="catImg1" alt="a cat" />
                    <img src="image/cat2.jpg" id="catImg2" alt="a cat" />
                    <img src="image/dog1.jpg" id="dogImg1" alt="a dog" />
                    <img src="image/dog2.jpg" id="dogImg2" alt="a dog" />
					</div>
              </div>
           </div> 
		</div>
	<div id="aboutMe">
	    <div id="aboutMeContainer">
	        <img src="image/dog1.jpg" id="aboutdogImg1" alt="a dog" />
	        <div id="aboutMeInfo">               
	           <h1> Chloe Jessee</h1>
	           <p> I LOVE PETS! I am excited to get to know yours. Here is a little about me. I am twelve years old, and I am an entrepreneur. I wanted to start a buisiness that would let me interact with pets. So I decided to try walking dogs. I am good with animals, and they usually love me. I am confident that I will be able to create a bond with your dog as we go on walks.  So go ahead and give me a chance, book an appointment today! <span class="listItems" id="setUp" style="color: blue" > Set Up Walking Appointment</sapn> </p>
	       </div>
	       <img src="image/cat1.jpg" id="aboutcatImg1" alt="a cat" />
	    </div>
	</div>	
	<div id="faqs">
	   <div id="faqsContianer">
           <div id="theFaqs">
	         <h2>What are my rates?</h2>
		     <p>$5.00 for single dog per 25 minute walk</p>
		     <p>$3.50 per dog for multiple dogs from same household.<p>
		     <h2>How do you pay me?</h2>
		     <p>I will accept cash after I complete the walk. In the future other payment options will be made available.<p>
		     <h2>What size of dog will I walk?</h2>
		     <p>Due to my age and size, I am only able to walk small to medium dogs at this time</p>
		     <h2>Where Will I walk your dog?</h2>
		     <p>I will stay within a 12 minute radius of your home<p>  
		</div>
		  <div class="petContainer">		
		     <div class="petCollage">
                <img src="image/dog3.jpg" id="dogImg3" alt="a dog" />
                <img src="image/cat1.jpg" id="catImg1" alt="a cat" />
                <img src="image/cat2.jpg" id="catImg2" alt="a cat" />
                <img src="image/dog1.jpg" id="dogImg1" alt="a dog" />
                <img src="image/dog2.jpg" id="dogImg2" alt="a dog" />
		     </div>
         </div>

	   </div>
	</div>
       
    </main>

</body>
</html>